  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Axona, you control a mysterious cube trapped in a strange dimension. Will you be able to find the way out?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/extras/7e7d771060def1e7a7bf36d9a9dabca3.poster.avif?t=1771764952\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/extras/7e7d771060def1e7a7bf36d9a9dabca3.webm?t=1771764952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/extras/7e7d771060def1e7a7bf36d9a9dabca3.mp4?t=1771764952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >72 Mind-twisting Levels</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roll the cube, get the keys and unlock the glyphs to advance to the next level. You will discover new mechanics and solve more complex puzzles as you progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/extras/a8268d2827949a4992345747a9d91a71.poster.avif?t=1771764952\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/extras/a8268d2827949a4992345747a9d91a71.webm?t=1771764952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/extras/a8268d2827949a4992345747a9d91a71.mp4?t=1771764952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play at your own pace</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Axona is designed to be a challenging puzzle game but can also be enjoyed in a relaxed manner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/extras/303fb67de454beca1a38bd9671880b47.poster.avif?t=1771764952\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/extras/303fb67de454beca1a38bd9671880b47.webm?t=1771764952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/extras/303fb67de454beca1a38bd9671880b47.mp4?t=1771764952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to solve each level within a limited number of moves...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/extras/d7dae3a99ab5e8f3633d1896533b97a4.poster.avif?t=1771764952\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/extras/d7dae3a99ab5e8f3633d1896533b97a4.webm?t=1771764952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/extras/d7dae3a99ab5e8f3633d1896533b97a4.mp4?t=1771764952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...Or take as many moves as you need.</p>",
